-- Evercore to Seek Buyers for MGM Advantage, Independent Reports
-- B y   T u h i n   K a r
-- 2012-07-14T10:56:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-14/evercore-to-seek-buyers-for-mgm-advantage-independent-reports.html
Evercore Partners Inc. (EVR)  was hired to
seek buyers for British insurer MGM Advantage, with a potential
sale price of 200 million pounds ($312 million), the Independent
newspaper  reported  today, without saying where it got the
information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
